with codecs.open('testdata/models/routing_matrix_multiple_starts.json',

    server_response = f.read()
responses.add(responses.GET,
    'https://matrix.route.ls.hereapi.com/routing/7.2/calculatematrix.json',
    server_response, status=200)

    expectedGeocoderResponse = f.read()

    'https://geocode.search.hereapi.com/v1/geocode',
    expectedGeocoderResponse, status=200)

    destination_waypoints=[[9.934574, -84.065544]])
self.assertTrue(response)
